{
    "info": {
        "name": "Smart School \u2014 Multi-School FINAL (all logins, 2 schools)",
        "description": "Explicit login for every role in both schools. Click any login and Send:\n- Staff (Admin/Teacher/Accountant): customapi/login/staffLogin (session).\n- Student/Parent: api/auth/login (returns token -> auto-stored in {{access_token}}).\nEach login sets {{school_id}} automatically. Then use folder 'Student data' with the stored token.\n\nSet {{base_url}} in the environment (e.g. http://localhost/smartschool).",
